  "title": "Architectural Assistants",
  "description": "<p>Scope of duties:-</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Able to handle the design for Building works and ensure Client Regulatory requirements are met.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To prepare 3D drawings in AutoCad and/or REVIT format for approval &amp; submission</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To schedule for Project activities and inspection, as to ensure that targeted completion dates are met.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To attend site meetings when required and co-ordinate with Clients, Consultants, Contractors, Vendors and relevant Authorities on</p>\n<p>all Project-related matters</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Familiar to prepare documents for different Authorities Submission via Coronet</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Must be meticulous in your work, a team player</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Able to do multi-tasking and handle various projects</p>",
